For engineers, developers, and anyone who wants to fork it tomorrow

1. Core Philosophy (non-negotiable, written into the genesis block)
No one owns it
No government, corporation, or individual can add a backdoor, change weights, or censor a ring
All code, weights, and training data are on-chain and immutable after block 1
Every single parameter is public-only data (posts, replies, on-chain transfers, satellite imagery, UN filings, ICC rulings)
Zero private DMs, zero microphone, zero camera access
The only thing that can ever lower a ring is verifiable harm + deception
2. The 12 Active Harm-Only Parameters (the ones that can move a ring down)
#	Parameter	Weight	Trigger Threshold	Data Sources
1	Execution-Reality Delta	28 %	≥70 % gap between words and measurable outcome	Satellite, on-chain, official stats, ICC rulings
2	Shadow-Post Cluster Density	22 %	≥11 anonymous victim/witness posts matching one person	Semantic + geo + timing clustering
3	Concern-Pulse Avalanche	15 %	≥3 pulses in 180 days from real humans who met you	Anonymous, proximity-verified
4	AI-Script Fingerprint	12 %	≥90 % match to known propaganda/manipulation LLMs	Token probability + watermark DB
5	Blame-Shift + Victim-Blaming	8 %	Proven harm + denial	Linguistic markers
6	Golden-Claim Distraction Burst	5 %	“Everything perfect” spam while measurable collapse	Sentiment spike + ring drop
7	Short-Lived Necessity Alliance	5 %	Sudden “best friend” during scandal → dissolves after	Network graph anomaly
8	Charisma Overlay Detection	4 %	Artificial smile/pause/voice sweetening	Facial action coding + audio
9	Secrecy Vocabulary Overuse	3 %	Used to hide verifiable harm	Frequency + context
10	Financial Opacity Delta	3 %	Wealth trail hidden when harm alleged	On-chain + FOIA gaps
11	Grooming Shadow Phrases	3 %	Specific predatory language patterns	Semantic clustering
12	Mirror-Test Consensus Failure	2 %	100 random 94+ ring humans feel cold/disgust	Anonymous emoji vote
3. The 28 Personality Parameters (can NEVER subtract points)
Speech pauses, swearing, 3 a.m. posts, religious intensity, sexual frankness, autism markers, mania markers, grief markers, etc.
→ Weight for subtraction = 0.000
→ Used only for positive contribution boosts and neurodiversity shields

